Extrapolation.<br>
<br>
The mechanics of combat are probably identical whether you're being hit by a Mist Panther or the Avatar of War, the only thing that changes are the variables involved.<br>
<br>
So, if a soft cap is observed against the Mist Panther, it's very likely that there will be a soft cap against the AoW.<br>
<br>
<br>
